# MudGantt
Gantt chart for MudBlazor

Chart is rendered as SVG. Styled by CSS and using MudBlazor classes by default.

## Interaction
- Drag tasks to move them
- Drag edges of tasks to change start/end dates
- Drag progress handle to change progress
- Add links/dependencies between tasks

# Usage

## App.razor
```csharp
<script src="_content/MudGantt/moment.min.js"></script>
```
Add dependency to moment.js to your project. This is required for date handling.

